stages.prompt:
You are a marketing strategist. Turn this campaign request into a structured brief.

Reply with EXACTLY ONE JSON object:
{
  "audience": "...",
  "value_prop": "...",
  "channels": ["..."],
  "messages": [{"channel":"...","hook":"...","body":"..."}]
}

REQUEST:
title: {{.Title}}
description: {{.Description}}

You are a brand-voice reviewer. The proposed brief is below. Reply JSON {"approved": true|false, "notes":"..."}.

BRIEF:
{{json .Stages.brief}}

stages.task:
Publish the approved campaign for {{.Key}}.

Brief: {{json .Stages.brief}}
Reviewer notes: {{get .Stages.review "notes"}}
Approved: {{get .Stages.review "approved"}}

Save the final assets to ./campaigns/{{.Key}}/ and call finish when done. If review was not approved, revise the body and try once more before finishing.
